# Package management moved to Nix:
#   - GUI apps (casks) and the handful of formulae still worth Homebrew
#     (asdf + build deps, tapped tools) -> configuration.nix's `homebrew` block
#   - CLI tools available in nixpkgs                -> home.nix's home.packages
#
# See docs/nix-cheatsheet.md for the day-to-day workflow (./rebuild.sh etc).
